OL,3,C'Intolerable': Investigation finds
OL,4,Cmisogyny and bullying in submarine
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FWomen in the submarine service were
OL,8,Fexposed to sexual harassment,
OL,9,Fmisogyny, bullying and rape, an
OL,10,Finvestigation by the Royal Navy has
OL,11,Ffound.
OL,13,FThe long-awaited investigation was
OL,14,Fordered in October 2022 after
OL,15,Fallegations by former lieutenant
OL,16,FSophie Brook, who described a
OL,17,F"constant campaign of sexual bullying".
