OL,4,Cmisogyny and bullying in submarine
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FMs Brook, who has since left the
OL,8,Fsubmarine service, said "multiple
OL,9,Fpeople" had contacted her with similar
OL,10,Fconcerns after she first went public
OL,11,Fwith her accusations.
OL,13,FThe allegations addressed in the
OL,14,Freport were from 2014 to 2020.
OL,16,FA heavily redacted final report of the
OL,17,Finvestigation into allegations across
OL,18,Fthe submarine service listed multiple
OL,19,Fincidents of abuse and harassment by
OL,20,Fmale submariners.
