OL,3,C'Intolerable': Investigation finds
OL,4,Cmisogyny and bullying in submarine
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FSome of them were senior officers,
OL,8,Fagainst their female colleagues.
OL,10,FAmong the most serious was "at least"
OL,11,Fone report of rape, while others
OL,12,Fincluded lewd comments and sexual
OL,13,Fgestures.
OL,15,FAdministrative action, "up to and
OL,16,Fincluding discharge from the Royal
OL,17,FNavy", has been taken against "several
OL,18,Findividuals", according to an
OL,19,Fexecutive summary published alongside
OL,20,Fthe full report.
