OL,3,C'Intolerable': Investigation finds
OL,4,Cmisogyny and bullying in submarine
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FThe head of the Royal Navy, Sir Ben
OL,8,FKey issued an unreserved public
OL,9,Fapology for the "intolerable" misogyny
OL,10,Fexposed within its ranks.
OL,12,FIn a statement published on Friday,
OL,13,FSir Ben said: "The investigation has
OL,14,Fconfirmed misogyny, bullying and other
OL,15,Funacceptable behaviours did occur
OL,16,Fduring the investigation period, and
OL,17,Fthis is intolerable.
OL,19,F"During the investigation process, Ms
OL,20,FBrook made several requests for
OL,21,Fredress.
